stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Pending
    Pending --> Processing : payment received
    Processing --> Shipped : items packed
    Processing --> Cancelled : out of stock
    Shipped --> Delivered : courier confirms
    Shipped --> Returned : customer refuses
    Delivered --> [*]
    Returned --> Refunded
    Cancelled --> Refunded
    Refunded --> [*]

    note right of Processing
        Inventory is locked while
        an order is in this state
    end note
